name: Friday Night Funkin' vs Impostor (Among Us) | FNF Mod | HTML 5 Online Port
name_original: Friday Night Funkin' vs Impostor (Among Us) | FNF Mod | HTML 5 Online Port
description:
Friday Night Funkin' vs Impostor is yet another fan-made full-week mod for the music rhythm game Friday Night Funkin'. He chewed up the upper half of Girlfriend's body and now he wants to kill Boyfriend, too. Ladies and gentlemen, please welcome Impostor from Among Us!

The downloadable version of the mod, on which this port is based, is available here. All the credit goes to Clowfoe.
